，潜在通胀的关键指标几乎没有变化。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;但好消息&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/_N5FiFUl6axKTjhHpIpkr-ADbVmfXnD_7qVU55rxi7bNU7RkTrJclTrGEYWaW_zSgnYw64K8ddojozqT_PAr3fIOZlsigXDYpuGvejaNEy-Ps-NwykzFx-crJyFyYd_kGf5YZwbzGh4RZTSc1oh_K-Zrq15BNu9_mdNRWfYauJrJINyTDsqhl-1sRVuxjwBe-d_XXUTK0O-iz17G4ZdfxyQjeZQuCylDoj8OLTdjKlllhhyRb456zUUHQLkQ7RknjEF-WA_usIDq5Uc0pst-aoIk9PUFCBpi7N4_w9wprqNPkJQMhcYfHUlz1zn_eOXJZVpCnkq0conSbbspA_n0xAp3_BwRNqmPLb19VOJYdPFhZ9QCjsTd6WHoGzWVChFhuqHrq-_f9NXqf6s8Y0WiwxHNuI9cFjN2gA_byT--xJ52vnu_RrPBnYhROPIpa5qWujURlsGSmlUrTpFJrK99qOjlPGMwNPKFoyrcRDfQR6Ge3wAI5UvB2W3mkRr1QGSe2Ky1uwDxNm59NQgYjwKb4DtOUMFoSw/OU4dZbIkwht8LqWQ1-LhPqpnG2XSXQJB/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="美国CPI自2020年以来首次下降，核心指标持平"&gt;不太可能持续下去&lt;/a&gt;，特别是在特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/kCICDr-zQ1-bQNdm1F1g-cPPPx7caxtZcdBALkENIUg9gcaY4FHCQaFD2vKteQNFyK2V7V5t7LOJHL52XNMC0pygD2_ZNt9tYutIWPHutvOsPzR-fcd4r53OxhrrlbRIwuFd9tYk9VlNs69ye0XSLuBrd1exu6Fjn7twYhtwFjtGQo4v5iPRao1PAJxwf0uzySq25Wela8M2maHWK5_naVorooArNsc-FglNXdxZkyFI3Xf_sOHgp7FSJ0cogOXBMyAKd1iSoi6N0oA6c6hlyt4FX2aMtbJJno7lyNEeA0mVZ2bQ-zMtO28KS9tf2SQIrxHhLmgQSfsaZWJdO3dFWvARaMaLEYExz5FhhJTTOpRrHPEiX_GoWIZoXIUnuOxlMLMFILonLyd1WOzseJKHSBRrFzuhmefEY5KmWno86RY1zrjpam27nTmR7FdcYu_iRe_NmeXBNrSCEEWK06hZIWwVSqVBrP8OYbXCQq922p3LH4KxelrWQbEg8DUVWo4ViQVI_rBtBDOsb-uqVRll_Ec2PfGx/A50rrUxEzS_ZfLwvar6GvOMSG_wbhs1T/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着袭击加剧、封锁重启，美伊休战破裂"&gt;决定再次开始轰炸伊朗&lt;/a&gt;之后。尽管月度数据温和，但年度指标继续表明通胀上升：总体指数较上年同期上涨 3.5%，核心指标上涨 2.6%。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; Inflation Insights 总裁奥迈尔·谢里夫 (Omair Sharif) 表示：“这种疲软可能是暂时的，下个月的报告发布后就会消失。”彭博经济研究的安德鲁·萨赫和特洛伊·杜里指出，这些数字可能&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/GI3NiCjbM2Ly1AsSRjzYv-3zaRcKaaBn2UzYjO_Bku09bTJV1eKMGULfxVSiHb9lKkxUjj6rzks_e1n-d3WY9ULcgS8C4XFJbK-aI