16px;"&gt;美国和伊朗之间的对峙提振了油价，霍尔木兹海峡冲突引发了人们对能源供应中断可能加剧通胀的担忧&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/nCzNamaoV4D7MxThD5p2YHcd4o9AjPoYeOOdR-Evi7EPSIC-4_uMovJjTq7i_mB1qWoMEaPxT7ezvo2G_BjQiwiOlheYc2hMLwkMvEwANmj6Q5fh1yZ1YGpFjTnKYwWywCy7USc6omAx6_WCS-xK8af6hfcU_F3njvjzl53irRyomtPaKudjT-ICv9jbfaY4mO40-etMXFK6hajqfjuqAx-l7jExmB5nzlf45fbZC7LtIGIV6ehkXCZWzD1W4RoBcsxLZHeJnmd1Hi3GZDSvbidsGnJOem7crlRXfJLPR_YzTyRaRrxqDj22xYniBUUZlPgWnpnuJpPswPSBimWZollanQksqDch6Kqf0halryTZKwk1Iihpsbd-PlD4B1ORYtkrdX8q54sZxDMsHlrRNLWl2tN8MLuluTOfGuN1dAkdquyK6Bci1-qixgF1Lh_MKi2Sp3WjHLdn9EZHTK6psAA3rU-B9yQ6OjXy9XrehUsnSjGXf9YdhesnPRR09_XshP8rg2X8K7Ch_OjfP2PDJqUm3w/czJ5F7THEjsly0-Z_HAYgBu2Vd2_xp67/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="油价上涨引发美联储加息押注，股市和债券下跌：市场结束"&gt;，股市和债券一起下跌&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;如果这听起来很熟悉，那是因为它确实如此。美国似乎无法从 4 1/2 个月前它帮助发动的战争中解脱出来。尽管美军再次发动袭击，伊朗仍在继续袭击美国盟友和国际航运。投资者可能希望临时和平协议能够成为永久性的，但运气不佳。结果，标准普尔 500 指数&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/xj9il67wepFU8atcLKQQV7hx7jGhWAomTzoPUvMy9IZFBx3-YbrMmIRqJO2rQBCibRRdlKIu4zOVxt83ZHFXFzHQbjIPtgORmnHdqLL5gmk_ua5rHGWj0L9oBdNpfXKuKGt4bHF0hJ1PWzwp8WH4fNESH82oPk5vsEBFSut2ikxfpDCbUAmHwVt6dzBntkirNTCKbehGViTCkX3O89PYR8OGqsH1gbI-lmHsNEF-t65WcInypoc3aVvJASRUzh4gMHfc9uIlP0sVK8Y5EfJs1Ub1uZtGn0J298rast2e8pezEihvXuLz1RUTyswv0eOmxvmPs7iJRC-n73WjLvVX5nSWdkTO90gBwStcFVIXlYfclyB3df8zNMoV8VCAABGfDwORDbsMaoOY-D-lDnZ1jt11l8JtKtrW9oG17SAiZfqBg3vK6V17jqOCEmV8Dfre4G0UJQO6vHa3ATcC6BKclDAsCbGybmqEGuW_D0ZqqwYYtJ141mAYCZWfo7fmJJoZkalY3iX4wY4NkFjpopxNKhYu3UUTEg/3WeJP2CYOd8dHesTWgN_nFX96o2VUDc-/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="韩国抛售后，SK 海力士 ADR 在第二个交易日暴跌"&gt;周一下跌&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;额外的附带损害可能是唐纳德·特朗普对美联储降息的希望。由于油价加剧了本已高企的通胀，货币市场本月上涨的可能性几乎相等。美联储理事克里斯托弗·沃勒表示，官员们&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/nTS34XecsMIF0W7FuiPE_QxUW9BJ